These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, lemonade
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: sports, disaster
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: tennis, skiing
The people use 2 different means of transport: skateboard, helicopter
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
2. the person drinking lemonade is in an even position##4
3. the person watching disaster movies is the person drinking cola##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | cola  | lemonade   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster     | sports   |
| Sport         | skiing | tennis |
| Transport     | skateboard | helicopter    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There 2 different types of food: pumpkin, watermelon
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: zombie, crime
2 different pets are kept: hedgehog, hamster
The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, bike
1. the owner of the hamster is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching zombie movies is the person driving the bike##1
3. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | pumpkin     | watermelon |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | zombie  |
| Pet           | hamster         | hedgehog     |
| Transport     | ship   | bike    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
