The people have 2 different jobs:  project-manager, writer
2 different pets are kept: mouse, fish
The people use 2 different means of transport: snowmobile, ship
1. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the writer##3
2. the owner of the fish is on the right of the writer##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Beverage    | water     | mirinda |
| Job         | writer | project-manager    |
| Pet         | mouse         | fish        |
| Transport   | snowmobile         | ship    |

