There 2 different types of food: lettuce, broccoli
The people have 2 different hobbies: video-games, sudoku
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: techno, punk
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
3. the fan of punk is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Beverage      | 7up     | milk |
| Food          | broccoli   | lettuce  |
| Hobby         | video-games | sudoku     |
| Music-Genre   | techno  | punk         |

