.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  scientist, entrepreneur
There are 2 different nationalities: chinese, polish
2 different pets are kept: rat, snake
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: volleyball, tennis
1. the person who's sport is tennis is in an even position##4
2. the polish is on the far left or far right##3
3. the entrepreneur is the chinese##1
4. the owner of the rat is on the left of the polish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Job           | entrepreneur | scientist    |
| Nationality   | chinese       | polish |
| Pet           | rat         | snake    |
| Sport         | volleyball    | tennis   |

